454
00:39:51,199 --> 00:39:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] To je avantura.

455
00:39:51,940 --> 00:39:53,679
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

456
00:39:53,679 --> 00:40:01,619
[SPEAKER_01] Sad lijepo dok slušate, uzmite Bibliju, stavite ispred sebe i čin završi ovaj epizoda, krenite.

457
00:40:01,619 --> 00:40:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] Jer naše misle stvarno nekad znaju biti autodestruktivne i onda znaš da to nije Božje.

458
00:40:08,800 --> 00:40:10,199
[SPEAKER_01] Njegove nikad nisu destruktivne.

459
00:40:10,199 --> 00:40:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

460
00:40:11,000 --> 00:40:17,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ako neko želi baš konkretan savjet, počnite sa psalmima.

461
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:24,840
