489
00:42:35,500 --> 00:42:38,699
[SPEAKER_00] taj fine tuning, da ga točno pronađeš.

490
00:42:38,699 --> 00:42:44,599
[SPEAKER_00] A to se događa u vježbi, kad si nostop u prisutnosti

491
00:42:44,599 --> 00:42:46,480
[SPEAKER_00] i kad se izlažeš tome.

492
00:42:46,480 --> 00:42:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti dolaziš iz otvorene priče,

493
00:42:49,500 --> 00:42:53,619
