495
00:42:56,440 --> 00:42:59,519
[SPEAKER_00] postoji velika šansa da ćeš propustiti.

496
00:42:59,519 --> 00:43:03,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali to Boga ne sprečava da ti on progovori preko prijateljice,

497
00:43:03,400 --> 00:43:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] preko nekog trajanja.

498
00:43:05,119 --> 00:43:07,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ne kažem da Bog samo progovara u tišini.

499
00:43:07,820 --> 00:43:10,980
[SPEAKER_00] Postoji jedan i biblijski model u psalmu 95,

500
00:43:10,980 --> 00:43:14,760
[SPEAKER_00] je zapravo govori kako Bogu pristupamo u molitvi.

501
00:43:15,619 --> 00:43:19,659
[SPEAKER_00] I onda imaš dosluce kasnije na zaušetku tog psalma

502
00:43:19,659 --> 00:43:21,320
[SPEAKER_00] da Bog objavi svoju riječ,

503
00:43:21,320 --> 00:43:23,480
[SPEAKER_00] ali već si prošao svu buku i hvalu,

504
00:43:23,480 --> 00:43:25,940
[SPEAKER_00] ušao si sa hvalama, s pjesmama

505
00:43:25,940 --> 00:43:28,199
[SPEAKER_00] i na kraju si i kleknuo,

506
00:43:28,199 --> 00:43:32,119
[SPEAKER_00] ali onda se u tišini događa njegova riječ koja je osobna.

507
00:43:32,119 --> 00:43:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da bi ja izazoo ljude u ovom užurbanom svijetu

508
00:43:35,699 --> 00:43:37,940
[SPEAKER_00] da probaju naći vrijeme tišine,

509
00:43:37,940 --> 00:43:40,079
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da nam toga baš fali.

510
00:43:40,079 --> 00:43:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] I kardinal Sarah je bio jako

511
00:43:44,440 --> 00:43:50,639
