[SPEAKER_01] da ne idem na jedno putovanje ili ne idem.

518
00:44:05,960 --> 00:44:07,780
[SPEAKER_01] I baš mi je bio nekakav ono,

519
00:44:07,780 --> 00:44:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] kao kažu na engleskom gut feeling

520
00:44:09,500 --> 00:44:14,840
