550
00:45:53,820 --> 00:45:55,519
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ljudi bi to trebali znaći.

551
00:45:55,519 --> 00:45:58,559
[SPEAKER_00] A to kažem, to je poznavanje riječi.

552
00:45:58,559 --> 00:46:00,519
