577
00:47:14,139 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je možda jako važno.

578
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] Osobito u karizmatskim zajednicama,

579
00:47:17,980 --> 00:47:18,940
[SPEAKER_00] u karizmatskoj struji.

580
00:47:18,940 --> 00:47:21,360
[SPEAKER_00] Da su stvari koje se događaju,

581
00:47:21,360 --> 00:47:24,460
[SPEAKER_00] da su programi, projekti, formacije,

582
00:47:24,460 --> 00:47:26,420
