1576
01:27:40,300 --> 01:27:41,180
[SPEAKER_00] i naravno tu sam,

1577
01:27:41,180 --> 01:27:44,640
[SPEAKER_00] to je bila još i post i molitva,

1578
01:27:44,640 --> 01:27:47,619
[SPEAKER_00] još i neki drugi videovi molitve,

1579
01:27:47,619 --> 01:27:50,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali ovo je nešto moje bilo.

1580
01:27:50,460 --> 01:27:53,479
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon toga dolazi dan,

1581
01:27:53,479 --> 01:27:54,699
[SPEAKER_00] dva, tri dana prije

1582
01:27:54,699 --> 01:27:56,539
[SPEAKER_00] i ništa se ne događa po tom pitanju.

1583
01:27:56,539 --> 01:27:58,340
[SPEAKER_00] Produkcija, sve znaju,

1584
01:27:58,340 --> 01:28:00,260
