1586
01:28:01,859 --> 01:28:03,779
[SPEAKER_00] to je jedan poslije drugi svijet na steđu.

1587
01:28:03,779 --> 01:28:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] Znači tu si gdje je tvoj x-ić,

1588
01:28:05,840 --> 01:28:06,300
[SPEAKER_01] nema mi cijeli.

1589
01:28:06,300 --> 01:28:07,100
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, tako je.

1590
01:28:07,100 --> 01:28:07,680
[SPEAKER_00] I to što znaš,

1591
01:28:07,680 --> 01:28:08,479
[SPEAKER_00] ako ideš negdje,

1592
01:28:08,479 --> 01:28:09,840
[SPEAKER_00] znaš zašto ideš,

1593
01:28:09,840 --> 01:28:10,479
[SPEAKER_00] kad ideš,

1594
01:28:10,479 --> 01:28:12,359
