1595
01:28:12,359 --> 01:28:13,760
[SPEAKER_00] četrdesetineš kamera je bilo.

1596
01:28:13,760 --> 01:28:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] Sve moralo biti,

1597
01:28:17,180 --> 01:28:18,680
[SPEAKER_00] onako, na visokoj razini.

1598
01:28:18,680 --> 01:28:21,239
[SPEAKER_00] I zadnji dan,

1599
01:28:21,239 --> 01:28:22,220
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo u jednom,

1600
01:28:22,220 --> 01:28:24,260
[SPEAKER_00] na jednom mjestu,

1601
01:28:24,260 --> 01:28:25,899
[SPEAKER_00] prije dolazka

1602
01:28:25,899 --> 01:28:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] u backstage na hipodrom.

1603
01:28:28,000 --> 01:28:30,199
[SPEAKER_00] I meni Marko dolazi,

1604
01:28:30,279 --> 01:28:31,479
[SPEAKER_00] to je možda bilo tri sata,

1605
01:28:31,479 --> 01:28:32,260
[SPEAKER_00] četiri prije,

1606
01:28:32,260 --> 01:28:33,060
[SPEAKER_00] i on meni kaže

1607
01:28:33,060 --> 01:28:35,840
[SPEAKER_00] da ima poticaj,

1608
01:28:35,840 --> 01:28:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ja trebao se obratiti ljudima,

1609
01:28:37,760 --> 01:28:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] da bi trebalo nešto reći ljudima.

1610
01:28:39,600 --> 01:28:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] I ja ti ne mogu pisati.

1611
01:28:42,319 --> 01:28:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] U tom trenutku prvo,

1612
01:28:43,380 --> 01:28:44,579
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam od sebe reagirao

1613
01:28:44,579 --> 01:28:44,960
[SPEAKER_00] i rekao,

1614
01:28:44,960 --> 01:28:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Marko, ja ne znam,

1615
01:28:45,859 --> 01:28:47,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili ja imam autoritet za to.

1616
01:28:47,380 --> 01:28:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] Ljudi su u tvoje ime došli ovdje,

1617
01:28:49,260 --> 01:28:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] na račun tvojeg imena,

1618
01:28:50,819 --> 01:28:52,680
[SPEAKER_00] su tu,

1619
01:28:52,680 --> 01:28:53,479
[SPEAKER_00] ne znam,

1620
01:28:53,479 --> 01:28:54,600
[SPEAKER_00] imam li autoritet uopće,

1621
01:28:54,600 --> 01:28:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] govori to ovim ljudima.

1622
01:28:56,000 --> 01:28:56,479
[SPEAKER_00] On kaže,

1623
01:28:56,479 --> 01:28:58,539
[SPEAKER_00] da bi ja trebao,

1624
01:28:58,539 --> 01:28:59,619
[SPEAKER_00] da misli da bi ja trebao.

1625
01:28:59,619 --> 01:29:01,380
[SPEAKER_00] I pitao mi ono,

1626
