[SPEAKER_00] što ti dolazi?

1627
01:29:02,140 --> 01:29:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] Iskreno,

1628
01:29:02,739 --> 01:29:03,539
[SPEAKER_00] odmah mi je došlo.

1629
01:29:03,539 --> 01:29:05,380
[SPEAKER_00] Odmah mi je došlo ono mislo,

1630
01:29:05,380 --> 01:29:06,220
[SPEAKER_00] koji je neki download.

1631
01:29:06,220 --> 01:29:07,520
[SPEAKER_00] I znao sam da je to milost,

1632
01:29:07,520 --> 01:29:08,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja je za taj trenut,

1633
01:29:08,539 --> 01:29:10,420
[SPEAKER_00] bila spremna ranije.

1634
01:29:11,380 --> 01:29:14,220
[SPEAKER_00] molitvam da se čahurilo nešto

1635
01:29:14,220 --> 01:29:14,979
[SPEAKER_00] i onda jednostavno,

1636
01:29:14,979 --> 01:29:15,399
[SPEAKER_00] kad je došlo,

1637
01:29:15,399 --> 01:29:16,180
[SPEAKER_00] to bi joj samo,

1638
01:29:16,180 --> 01:29:18,260
[SPEAKER_00] a mogu podijeliti odmah,

1639
01:29:18,260 --> 01:29:19,460
[SPEAKER_00] što mi je došlo.

1640
01:29:19,460 --> 01:29:20,859
[SPEAKER_00] I uglavnom,

1641
01:29:20,859 --> 01:29:21,119
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam,

1642
