1646
01:29:28,319 --> 01:29:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dok smo bili pod policijskom pratnjem,

1647
01:29:29,659 --> 01:29:29,960
[SPEAKER_00] ja njemu,

1648
01:29:29,960 --> 01:29:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] e, poslao sam ti poruku,

1649
01:29:30,960 --> 01:29:31,319
[SPEAKER_00] kao,

1650
01:29:31,319 --> 01:29:32,159
[SPEAKER_00] pročitaj.

1651
01:29:32,159 --> 01:29:33,840
[SPEAKER_00] I ja sam upravo napisao,

1652
01:29:33,840 --> 01:29:34,760
[SPEAKER_00] šta bi ja izrekao.

1653
01:29:34,760 --> 01:29:36,960
[SPEAKER_00] Kad smo došli u backstage,

1654
01:29:36,960 --> 01:29:37,739
[SPEAKER_00] na hipodromu,

1655
01:29:37,739 --> 01:29:38,539
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je,

1656
01:29:39,500 --> 01:29:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] moj zadnji pokušaj je da ja kažem,

1657
01:29:40,739 --> 01:29:42,739
[SPEAKER_00] Marko, možda bi ti to trebalo reći.

1658
01:29:42,739 --> 01:29:44,560
[SPEAKER_00] I onda me je rekao da on to ne može reći,

1659
01:29:44,560 --> 01:29:46,520
[SPEAKER_00] jer mislim da bi ja to trebalo reći.

1660
01:29:46,520 --> 01:29:48,239
[SPEAKER_00] I nismo se dogovorili

1661
01:29:48,239 --> 01:29:49,579
[SPEAKER_00] bez da je produkcija znala.

1662
01:29:49,579 --> 01:29:50,920
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, u tom svemu,

1663
01:29:50,920 --> 01:29:52,260
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je svak morao znaći sve,

1664
01:29:52,260 --> 01:29:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] ja svojmi putem ispričavam

1665
01:29:54,199 --> 01:29:55,380
[SPEAKER_00] producentu koncerta,

1666
01:29:55,380 --> 01:29:57,159
[SPEAKER_00] što mu nismo to rekli.

1667
01:29:57,159 --> 01:30:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] Marko je rekao da nakon neću izvati ja,

1668
01:30:01,119 --> 01:30:02,779
[SPEAKER_00] da on misli da bi ja trebalo imati

1669
01:30:02,779 --> 01:30:04,579
[SPEAKER_00] nekakav intervent.

1670
01:30:04,579 --> 01:30:06,520
[SPEAKER_00] I mogu samo zamisliti

1671
