1675
01:30:12,699 --> 01:30:13,680
[SPEAKER_00] Ahtum, ahtum.

1676
01:30:13,680 --> 01:30:15,779
[SPEAKER_00] Šta ovaj sad radi?

1677
01:30:15,779 --> 01:30:16,720
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom,

1678
01:30:16,720 --> 01:30:18,579
[SPEAKER_00] znači, bilo jako spontano.

1679
01:30:18,579 --> 01:30:20,899
[SPEAKER_00] Nije bilo zamisljeno ranije.

1680
01:30:20,899 --> 01:30:22,579
[SPEAKER_00] Mi nismo znali kako ćemo to izvesti.

1681
01:30:23,760 --> 01:30:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] A ono što mi je došlo,

1682
01:30:24,800 --> 01:30:26,300
[SPEAKER_00] znači, kad je on mene to pitao,

1683
01:30:26,300 --> 01:30:27,939
[SPEAKER_00] onaj prvi osjećaj taj,

1684
01:30:27,939 --> 01:30:28,319
[SPEAKER_00] ja kažem,

1685
01:30:28,319 --> 01:30:28,979
[SPEAKER_00] kod download,

1686
01:30:28,979 --> 01:30:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] kada stisneš i spusti se.

1687
01:30:30,640 --> 01:30:32,520
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam ti imao sliku

1688
