1719
01:31:27,260 --> 01:31:28,819
[SPEAKER_00] da izraze vrijernost Bogu.

1720
01:31:28,819 --> 01:31:30,420
[SPEAKER_00] I to je nešto što je

1721
01:31:30,420 --> 01:31:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] meni došlo na srce.

1722
01:31:31,500 --> 01:31:32,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja si kontam,

1723
